column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, m.z, m.logMass FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObjAll s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort m ON m.specObjID = s.specObjID ORDER BY x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
